lead_paragraph: Bayern Munich will not be deterred by what the club say are false reports of discontent in coach Pep Guardiola's team as they focus on becoming the first side to win a fourth straight Bundesliga title.

headline.print_headline: Magical Four Driving Bayern in Guardiola Swansong
